lock\"><span style = \"font-weight:bold;\">Registration<\/span><\/div><div class = \"text-block\">The trial was registered at University Hospital Medical Information Network centre (UMIN000028317). The trial was also ethically reviewed and approved by Tohoku University Hospital Ethical Committee (2017-2-213 (Application-8996)) on 2 December 2017.<\/div><\/div>","changed_on":1613232362}